description.narrative: New Element, which contributes to Children In Urban Settings / Local Governance, Cross-Sectoral Monitoring, Data And Situation Analyses, Equitable Access To Quality Education, Learning Outcomes, Other Cross-Sectoral Programme Areas, Prevention And Response Services For Violence Against Children, Prevention And Response Services For Violence Against Children (Covid), Social Protection. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Advocacy And Public Engagement, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: The social inclusion of all children and adolescents, especially vulnerable ones, is supported by quality, equitable and coordinated health, education and child protection systems and protective social norms.
